node.text:
Normally we do not get political, but the fire situation is so dire and the destruction so heartbreaking that we feel the need to speak up.  MAFFS (which quickly converts aircraft into firefighting machines) is one of the best solutions governments and industry can further support in the battle against wildfires.  It is a proven resource that can add capacity faster than any other and our people need effective support as quickly as possible. 

If you are in one of the countries affected by wildfire consider reaching out to your elected representatices to let them know about it.
